---
title: Hearty Cheesy Plant-Based Mince & Mushroom Pie with Baby Leaves & Potato Topping
description: There’s no need to wait in line at the bakery to get your hands on a comforting pie when you can whip one up at home in no time. For the filling, bake a saucy veggie mince with mushrooms and greens then spread over a mash potato top. There you have it, one tasty pie straight from your own oven!

